The Imps

I actually think “imps” is a better metaphor than henchmen.

An imp is:

* small
* mischievous
* specialized
* cheap
* numerous

One imp isn’t impressive.

Ten thousand coordinated imps become powerful.

Examples:

* indexing imp
* tagging imp
* citation imp
* provenance imp
* graph imp
* formatting imp
* SEO imp
* translation imp
* curiosity imp
* duplicate finder

Each has one simple mission.

